data.title: In Person and Virtual Dance Classes at Gibney
data.meta_description: Explore Gibney's class schedule! Daily dance classes in-person at our New York City studios and online for dancers around the world.
data.text:
See the current class schedule below for information on dates, times, locations and cancellations.

Please review Gibney’s Plan Your Visit page for our current COVID-19 safety policies.

Classes are held at both Gibney 890 and 280 locations. Please check the class description and title to confirm the class location.

Please visit our Education FAQ for any questions you may have about in-person class policies and pricing. See Gibney’s Plan Your Visit page for our current COVID-19 safety policies.

For questions, please contact us at classes@gibneydance.org, or call 646.837.6809.

Follow us on Instagram at @gibneyeducation for class highlights and more!
